'''Kitik Keed'kak''' was a [[Yam'rii/Legends|Yam'rii]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Huk/Legends|Huk]].

==Biography==
In [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]]<ref name="The New Essential Chronology">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''</ref> she was in [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina]] during [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi's]] visit,<ref name="Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope">{{Film|IV}}</ref> where her multifacted eye was scoping out [[Kal'Falnl C'ndros]]' brood of [[Egg/Legends|eggs]] with covetous intent.<ref name="DB" /> She later followed [[Kal'Falnl C'ndros]] outside, hoping she would lead her to her nest. Keed'kak was friends with [[Swilla Corey]] during those visits.

==Personality and traits==
Kitik Keed'kak had a bad temper and could be made angry very easily. She was strong given her tiny frame, and was known for her stealthiness. Keed'kak was also very good with technology. Her diet consisted of meat<ref name="CCG" /> and fresh eggs.<ref name="DB" />

